INSERT INTO `listings` VALUES ('012709e1-53ed-406a-bfd9-682458a3ae02','99999999-9999-9999-9999-999999999999','Gently used size 7 running shoes with textured grip sole suitable for daily campus walking and everyday hostel-to-campus movement','These size 7 running shoes have mainly been used for daily campus walking around the BITS campus and have not been worn for intense training or rough trekking. The textured grip sole provides reasonable cushioning and grip on regular campus pathways, mess corridors and hostel stairs. The upper material is still in decent shape with only typical creases from walking and a few minor marks that can be cleaned off with basic shoe care.\n\nThe insole is comfortable enough for daily wear during classes and informal outings, and there is no visible tearing or separation around the toe area. Laces and eyelets are intact, and the shoes still feel structurally sound. These make for a practical extra pair if you want something comfortable and inexpensive to rotate with your primary footwear, especially for long days that involve moving between departments, hostels, and sports grounds.',1710.00,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,0,NULL,NULL,'Fashion','2025-09-28 05:01:04','2025-09-28 05:01:04'),('020a94ff-fb33-429f-ae84-a5548320d802','33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333','Hostel-friendly air cooler with approx 20L tank, 3 fan speeds and regular motor ideal for cooling small hostel rooms in summer','This air cooler has been used for a couple of summers in a BITS-style hostel room and does a decent job of keeping the room more comfortable during the hotter months. The water tank capacity is around 20 litres, which is enough for several hours of continuous use before requiring a refill, depending on fan speed and outside temperature. With 3 selectable fan speeds and adjustable swing, you can choose between a quieter breeze for night-time use or stronger airflow for afternoons.\n\nThe unit runs on an regular motor and works with regular hostel or PG po